111
00:18:12.480 --> 00:18:18.780
Abhirath Batra: Right, so who is a user asks the question, who… Oh…

112
00:18:20.060 --> 00:18:22.469
Abhirath Batra: Are you who you say you are?

113
00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:31.480
Abhirath Batra: And this question is obviously answered typically by passwords.

114
00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:40.159
Abhirath Batra: and other things, right? You click on a link on your email to tell the service that you are who you say you are. That's one part of it.

115
00:18:40.560 --> 00:18:47.730
Abhirath Batra: The second part of it is, what… Are you authorized to do?

