00:19:00.430 --> 00:19:17.040
Abhirath Batra: And there's people who are listening who are authorized to listen, but to sit in. And then there's other people who are not even authorized to attend this Zoom session, right? So, these are the two things that who is the user aspect of productionizing will answer.

118
00:19:18.190 --> 00:19:21.020
Abhirath Batra: The second thing is, what is their state?

